      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i mean the doctor just wrote a prescription, they don't actually know my body like i do. if the symptom is gone, isn't that the most important indicator? i've heard that taking too many antibiotics actually messes up your gut microbiome for a long time. wouldn't it be better to just stop once the skin looks normal to avoid that damage?",
